        <p>
          <span class="first-letter">A</span>msterdam is a captivating city,
          renowned for its picturesque canals, vibrant neighborhoods, and rich
          cultural heritage. Visitors can explore iconic museums like the Van
          Gogh Museum and the Anne Frank House, savor delicious local cuisine,
          and soak in the charm of historic architecture. Biking through its
          bike-friendly streets and visiting lively markets add to the unique
          experiences that make this city so special. With stunning visuals and
          a dynamic atmosphere, Amsterdam is a destination full of inspiration
          and adventure.
        </p>
