                  American pancakes, often served with a variety of sweet or
                  savory toppings. Common sweet options include powdered sugar,
                  fruit, or syrup, while savory varieties might feature cheese,
                  bacon, or vegetables.<br />
                  You can find dedicated pancake houses throughout the city,
                  where you can customize your meal. Whether enjoyed as
                  breakfast, lunch, or dessert, Dutch pancakes are a must-try
                  when visiting Amsterdam!
                </p>
